<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
{% include '_partials/seo' with { legacyTemplate: 'u-pull-parts.html' } %}
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"><link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Saira:ital,wght@0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;1,600;1,700;1,800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="kikers.css?v=20260713-craftcms3">
</head>
<body id="top">

{% include '_partials/site-header' with { navActive: 'parts', thirdHref: '#how', ctaLabel: 'Search Inventory', ctaHref: '#search' } %}

<nav class="crumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb"><div class="wrap"><a href="index.html">Home</a><span class="sep">›</span><span>Pull Your Own Parts</span></div></nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero compact" id="search">
  <div class="hero-photo ph ph--dark"><div class="ph-tag"><span class="kk">📷 HERO BACKGROUND</span><span class="d">Customer pulling a part in an organized row of the yard — daylight.</span></div></div>
  <div class="wrap"><div class="hero-grid">
    <div>
      <div class="h-tags"><span class="eyebrow on-ink">Self-Service Yard</span><span class="chiplet">Bring your tools</span><span class="chiplet">Flat-rate pricing</span></div>
      <h1>Pull your own parts. <em>Save big.</em></h1>
      <p class="lede">Kiker's is a self-service yard in Pensacola, organized by section and row. Search what's in the yard, bring your own tools, pull the part you need, and pay flat-rate pricing at the counter. Open Mon-Fri, 9 AM to 4:30 PM; Sat, 8 AM to 2 PM.</p>
      <div class="cta-row"><a class="btn btn--amber btn--lg" href="#inventory"><span class="ic">⌕</span>Search Inventory</a><a class="btn btn--outline-light btn--lg" href="contact.html">Plan Your Visit</a></div>
    </div>
    <div class="offer-card">
      <div class="ohead"><h2>Find a vehicle</h2></div>
      <div class="sub">Search by make and model — what's listed is in the yard.</div>
      <form class="qf" onsubmit="event.preventDefault();toast('Inventory search connects to Crush on the live site.');">
        <input type="text" placeholder="Search — “F-150 mirror”, “Civic engine”…" aria-label="Search parts">
        <div class="grid2"><input type="text" placeholder="Make"><input type="text" placeholder="Model"></div>
        <button class="btn btn--filled btn--block" type="submit"><span class="ic">⌕</span>Search the Yard</button>
      </form>
      <div class="fine">Inventory updated as vehicles arrive</div>
    </div>
  </div></div>
</section>
<div class="hazard"></div>

<!-- CHROME PLATES -->
<section class="sec tight">
  <div class="wrap"><div class="plates">
    <div class="plate"><div><div class="n" style="color:var(--red)">By Row</div><div class="l">Organized Yard</div></div></div>
    <div class="plate"><div><div class="n" style="color:var(--ink)">Flat-Rate</div><div class="l">Parts Pricing</div></div></div>
    <div class="plate"><div><div class="n" style="color:var(--ink)">BYO</div><div class="l">Tools &amp; Gloves</div></div></div>
    <div class="plate"><div><div class="n" style="color:var(--amber)">Weekly</div><div class="l">New Arrivals</div></div></div>
  </div></div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="sec" id="how" style="background:var(--surface-3)">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head center"><span class="eyebrow">How It Works</span><h2>Search · Pull · Save</h2><p>Three steps, and the savings are yours.</p></div>
    <div class="steps3">
      <div class="stepc"><div class="node">1</div><h3>Search</h3><p>Check the online inventory or browse the yard. Vehicles are sorted by section and row.</p></div>
      <div class="stepc"><div class="node">2</div><h3>Pull</h3><p>Bring your own tools and gloves and pull the parts you need. Staff on site if you need a hand.</p></div>
      <div class="stepc"><div class="node">3</div><h3>Save</h3><p>Pay flat-rate pricing at the counter — a fraction of buying new.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INVENTORY -->
<section class="sec" id="inventory">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head"><div class="row-between"><div><span class="eyebrow">In the Yard</span><h2 style="font-style:italic">What's on the lot now</h2></div><a class="btn btn--text" href="#search">Search inventory →</a></div></div>
    <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;margin-bottom:24px">
      <button class="chip" aria-pressed="true">Ford</button><button class="chip" aria-pressed="false">Chevy</button><button class="chip" aria-pressed="false">Toyota</button><button class="chip" aria-pressed="false">Honda</button><button class="chip" aria-pressed="false">Nissan</button><button class="chip" aria-pressed="false">Dodge / Ram</button>
    </div>
    <div class="fcards">
      <div class="feature-card"><div class="img"><span class="ph-mini">PHOTO: F-150</span></div><span class="flag">JUST IN</span><div class="fc-txt"><span class="avail" style="margin-bottom:8px"><span class="dot pulse"></span>In the yard now</span><h4>2011 Ford F-150</h4><span class="km">ROW 22 · 5.0L V8</span></div></div>
      <div class="feature-card"><div class="img"><span class="ph-mini">PHOTO: Civic</span></div><span class="flag">JUST IN</span><div class="fc-txt"><h4>2012 Honda Civic</h4><span class="km">ROW 14 · 1.8L · AUTO</span></div></div>
      <div class="feature-card"><div class="img"><span class="ph-mini">PHOTO: Silverado</span></div><span class="flag">HOT PART</span><div class="fc-txt"><span class="km">ENGINE · 5.3L V8</span><h4>'08 Silverado</h4></div></div>
      <div class="feature-card"><div class="img"><span class="ph-mini">PHOTO: Altima</span></div><span class="flag">JUST IN</span><div class="fc-txt"><h4>2009 Nissan Altima</h4><span class="km">ROW 18 · 2.5L</span></div></div>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:32px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.4fr 1fr;gap:32px;align-items:start">
      <div class="list">
        <div class="li"><div class="av">F</div><div class="tx"><div class="t1">2011 Ford F-150</div><div class="t2">Crew cab · 5.0L V8</div></div><div class="meta">ROW 22</div></div>
        <div class="li"><div class="av steel">H</div><div class="tx"><div class="t1">2012 Honda Civic</div><div class="t2">1.8L · Auto</div></div><div class="meta">ROW 14</div></div>
        <div class="li"><div class="av">C</div><div class="tx"><div class="t1">2008 Chevy Silverado</div><div class="t2">5.3L V8</div></div><div class="meta">ROW 07</div></div>
        <div class="li"><div class="av steel">T</div><div class="tx"><div class="t1">2010 Toyota Sequoia</div><div class="t2">4WD · 4.7L V8</div></div><div class="meta">ROW 31</div></div>
        <div class="li"><div class="av">N</div><div class="tx"><div class="t1">2009 Nissan Altima</div><div class="t2">2.5L · Auto</div></div><div class="meta">ROW 18</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="spec-card">
        <div class="sc-top"><div><h4>2012 Honda Civic LX</h4><span class="avail" style="margin-top:6px"><span class="dot"></span>In the yard</span></div><span class="row-tag">ROW 14</span></div>
        <div class="spec-grid">
          <div class="cell"><div class="ic">⛽</div><span class="lab">Engine</span><span class="val">1.8L</span></div>
          <div class="cell"><div class="ic">⏱</div><span class="lab">Mileage</span><span class="val">112k</span></div>
          <div class="cell"><div class="ic">⚙</div><span class="lab">Trans</span><span class="val">Auto</span></div>
          <div class="cell"><div class="ic">📅</div><span class="lab">Arrived</span><span class="val">Jun 12</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="sc-foot"><span class="hint">Parts priced in-yard</span><a class="btn btn--amber btn--sm" href="contact.html">Get directions</a></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="src" style="margin-top:16px">Live inventory connects to Crush on the built site. <span class="tagph">Crush embed goes here</span></p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="race-rule"></div>

<!-- YARD MAP -->
<section class="sec" style="background:var(--surface-3)">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head center"><span class="eyebrow">Find Your Way</span><h2 style="font-style:italic">Yard map</h2><p>Sorted by manufacturer into clean rows, so you know right where to head.</p></div>
    <div class="mapwrap" style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 900 320" role="img" aria-label="Stylized yard map showing rows by manufacturer" style="width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:4px">
        <rect width="900" height="320" fill="#eef0f2"/>
        <rect x="20" y="20" width="860" height="40" fill="var(--ink)"/>
        <text x="40" y="46" font-family="Saira, sans-serif" font-style="italic" font-weight="800" fill="#fff" font-size="20">KIKER'S U-PULL-IT · YARD MAP</text>
        <text x="800" y="45" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="12" fill="#FFC74D">GATE ▸</text>
        <g font-family="Saira, sans-serif" font-style="italic" font-weight="800" font-size="15" fill="#fff" text-anchor="middle">
          <rect x="40" y="90" width="120" height="190" rx="4" fill="#3a3137"/><text x="100" y="190">FORD</text><text x="100" y="210" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#FFC74D">ROWS 1–8</text>
          <rect x="180" y="90" width="120" height="190" rx="4" fill="#2a2630"/><text x="240" y="190">CHEVY</text><text x="240" y="210" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#FFC74D">ROWS 9–16</text>
          <rect x="320" y="90" width="120" height="190" rx="4" fill="#3a3137"/><text x="380" y="190">TOYOTA</text><text x="380" y="210" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#FFC74D">ROWS 17–22</text>
          <rect x="460" y="90" width="120" height="190" rx="4" fill="#2a2630"/><text x="520" y="190">HONDA</text><text x="520" y="210" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#FFC74D">ROWS 23–28</text>
          <rect x="600" y="90" width="120" height="190" rx="4" fill="#3a3137"/><text x="660" y="183">NISSAN /</text><text x="660" y="200">IMPORT</text><text x="660" y="220" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#FFC74D">ROWS 29–34</text>
          <rect x="740" y="90" width="120" height="190" rx="4" fill="#8C0C14"/><text x="800" y="183">DOMESTIC /</text><text x="800" y="200">MISC</text><text x="800" y="220" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#FFC74D">ROWS 35+</text>
        </g>
      </svg>
      <p class="src" style="margin-top:10px;padding:0 4px">Illustrative layout — replace with Kiker's real section/row map (and a drone aerial). <span class="tagph">yard map graphic</span></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- YARD RULES + HOURS -->
<section class="sec">
  <div class="wrap"><div class="split2 top">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">Before You Come</span>
      <h2 style="font-size:clamp(23px,3vw,31px);margin:8px 0 12px;font-style:italic">Yard rules</h2>
      <ul class="policies" style="border:none;padding:0;margin:0"><div style="display:grid;gap:12px">
        <li>🧰 <span>Bring your own tools and gloves — it's self-serve.</span></li>
        <li>👟 <span>Closed-toe shoes required; 16 and up on the yard.</span></li>
        <li>⚠️ <span>Watch for heavy steel, sharp metal and fluids.</span></li>
        <li>🏷️ <span>Parts are priced flat-rate at the counter.</span></li>
      </div></ul>
      <div style="margin-top:20px;display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap"><a class="btn btn--filled" href="contact.html"><span class="ic">📍</span>Get Directions</a><a class="btn btn--outline" href="tel:{{ siteSettings.phoneNumber|replace({"-": ""}) }}">Call the Yard</a></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hours">
      <h3>Hours</h3>
      <table class="htable" id="htable">
        <tr data-d="1"><td class="day">Monday</td><td class="hrs">9:00 – 4:30</td></tr>
        <tr data-d="2"><td class="day">Tuesday</td><td class="hrs">9:00 – 4:30</td></tr>
        <tr data-d="3"><td class="day">Wednesday</td><td class="hrs">9:00 – 4:30</td></tr>
        <tr data-d="4"><td class="day">Thursday</td><td class="hrs">9:00 – 4:30</td></tr>
        <tr data-d="5"><td class="day">Friday</td><td class="hrs">9:00 – 4:30</td></tr>
        <tr data-d="6"><td class="day">Saturday</td><td class="hrs">8:00 – 2:00</td></tr>
        <tr data-d="0"><td class="day">Sunday</td><td class="hrs">Closed</td></tr>
      </table>
      <div class="last">Last admission 30 minutes before close.</div>
      <div class="pays"><span class="pc">VISA</span><span class="pc">MC</span><span class="pc">AMEX</span><span class="pc">DISC</span><span class="pc">CASH</span></div>
    </div>
  </div></div>
</section>

<div class="race-rule"></div>
<section class="finalcta"><div class="wrap">
  <div><h2>Need a part? Come pull it.</h2><p>Organized rows, flat-rate pricing, big savings. Open Mon-Fri, 9 AM to 4:30 PM; Sat, 8 AM to 2 PM.</p></div>
  <div class="grp"><a class="btn btn--amber btn--lg" href="#search"><span class="ic">⌕</span>Search Inventory</a><a class="btn btn--outline-light btn--lg" href="contact.html">Get Directions</a></div>
</div></section>

